00:39:12,684 --> 00:39:14,250
You're bluffing.

743
00:39:14,285 --> 00:39:17,503
Bill Landry has a
contract with St. John's.

744
00:39:17,538 --> 00:39:19,149
A contract his lawyers
say he can get out of

