00:39:46,635 --> 00:39:49,235
I'm chief resident.

754
00:39:49,270 --> 00:39:51,604
And I'm gonna do
whatever I think is best

755
00:39:51,639 --> 00:39:54,540
for my patients
here at Chastain.

756
00:39:57,328 --> 00:39:59,862
I love it. Yes, yes.

757
00:39:59,897 --> 00:40:02,098
I can't believe
you pulled this off.

758
00:40:02,133 --> 00:40:04,145
I wish I could've seen the
