00:40:16,981 --> 00:40:18,959
Like ousting our
corporate overlords.

765
00:40:18,983 --> 00:40:20,762
- Which won't be an easy task.
- True,

766
00:40:20,786 --> 00:40:24,453
but we will get
it done, together.

767
00:40:24,489 --> 00:40:26,105
Agreed.

768
00:40:26,140 --> 00:40:31,511
But first, we need to do
something about your wardrobe.

769
00:40:34,115 --> 00:40:35,814
Welcome home, Conrad.

770
00:40:41,122 --> 00:40:43,506
Yeah! All right.

771
00:40:44,993 --> 00:40:48,178
Yeah!

772
00:40:51,466 --> 00:40:52,448
- Mwah.
- Thank you.

773
00:40:52,484 --> 00:40:53,800
Still looks good.

774
00:40:53,852 --> 00:40:55,802
A toast.

775
00:40:55,837 --> 00:40:58,654
Here's to another
day in the trenches.

776
00:40:58,690 --> 00:41:00,334
