777
00:41:00,358 --> 00:41:03,037
- Cheers. Cheers.
- It's good to have you back.

778
00:41:03,061 --> 00:41:05,644
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

779
00:41:10,401 --> 00:41:15,171
I'm sorry I wasn't there
to celebrate with you.

780
00:41:15,206 --> 00:41:17,156
After the day you've had,

781
00:41:17,191 --> 00:41:19,270
I'm the last person
