793
00:41:51,943 --> 00:41:56,078
I think we are good to go.

794
00:41:56,113 --> 00:41:58,480
Well, if you need anything...

795
00:41:58,516 --> 00:42:00,349
Yeah.

796
00:42:02,337 --> 00:42:04,888
Hey, so... you-you think
this place in Savannah,

797
00:42:04,923 --> 00:42:07,089
you really, you really
